text: "Born to Fly" is a 2000 song by country singer Sara Evans and is the title track from her third studio album Born to Fly. It went to number 74 in the United States, number 1 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs charts and number 7 on the Canadian RPM Country Tracks charts. ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Country songs Category:Sara Evans songs Category:Danielle Bradbery songs
